intent.user_query: List the details of service tickets created in the year 2023.

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT TicketID, CustomerID, ProductID, TicketDate, IssueDescription, Status, ResolutionDate FROM fitness_db.ServiceTickets WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM TicketDate) = 2023;

arguments.sql: SELECT TicketID, CustomerID, ProductID, TicketDate, IssueDescription, Status, ResolutionDate FROM fitness_db.ServiceTickets WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM TicketDate) = 2023;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
